item.description:
The Massachusetts Chapter of the National Oath Keepers Association
will be meeting on SUNDAY FEBRUARY 10th at 7pm

MEETING LOCATION: Liberty Clubhouse (Osgood Bradley Bldg),
18 Grafton Street (4th floor), Worcester, Massachusetts
...
Oath Keepers is a non-partisan association of current and
formerly serving military, reserves, National Guard, veterans,
Peace Officers, and Fire Fighters who will fulfill the Oath we
swore, with the support of like minded citizens who take an
Oath to stand with us, to support and defend the Constitution
against all enemies, foreign and domestic, so help us God.
Our Oath is to the Constitution. Our motto is "Not on our watch!"

PLEASE JOIN US ON SUNDAY FEBRUARY 10th at 7pm
item.name: Oath Keepers Meeting
